			"styles": "\n\t/* identity escapes keep the backslash in the AST name */\n\t#\\? {\n\t\tcolor: red;\n\t}\n\t.\\@ {\n\t\tcolor: blue;\n\t}\n\ta\\+b {\n\t\tcolor: green;\n\t}\n\t/* hex escapes decode (with optional whitespace terminator) */\n\t#\\3A b {\n\t\tcolor: orange;\n\t}\n\t/* mixed identity and hex in one name */\n\t.a\\?\\41 b {\n\t\tcolor: purple;\n\t}\n",
